<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Session Invite</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        table {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #007bff, #00c6ff);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #333;
            margin: 0 0 10px;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .details {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            table {
                width: 100%;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .header {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
            .footer {
                font-size: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <td class="header">
                <h1>You're Invited!</h1>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="content">
                <h2>Hello,</h2>
                <p>We are excited to invite you to the session titled <strong>Welcome to Your Computer Journey UOB</strong>.</p>
                <div class="details">
                    <p><strong>Location:</strong> University of Al-Mustaqbal</p>
                    <p><strong>Date:</strong> Tuesday, February 4th, 2025</p>
                    <p><strong>Time:</strong> 11:00 AM</p>
                </div>
                <p>This is a fantastic opportunity to learn, grow, and connect with others in the field of technology.</p>
                <p>We hope to see you there!</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="footer">
                <p>&copy; 2024 Byterun. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p>
                    <a href="https://facebook.com">Facebook</a> | 
                    <a href="https://twitter.com">Twitter</a>
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
